# Post-change checks

After a big batch of changes:
- Run lint/format with `./run checks`
- Fix any problems until the run passes
- Run a build with `./run app -b`
- Fix any errors or warnings until the run passes
- If reporting to the user, give a succinct summary of what passed, one line at most
